"If I am mad, it is mercy! May the gods pity the man who in his callousness can remain sane to the hideous end!"

–H.P. Lovecraft, The Temple

The mind recoils at the thought of the tenth deluxe expansion for Call of Cthulhu: The Card Game, or at least it should… In The Mark of Madness, Artists create works that seem to make no sense, even though many of their works share
